{"id":1525,"date":"2013-08-28T21:23:54","date_gmt":"2013-08-28T21:23:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/?p=1525"},"modified":"2019-02-21T13:40:47","modified_gmt":"2019-02-21T13:40:47","slug":"why-tell-stories","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/why-tell-stories\/","title":{"rendered":"Why Tell Stories?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"fl-builder-content fl-builder-content-1525 fl-builder-global-templates-locked\" data-post-id=\"1525\"><div class=\"fl-row fl-row-full-width fl-row-bg-none fl-node-58b370b1ac2b9 fl-row-bg-attachment-scroll\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac2b9\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-row-content-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-row-content fl-row-fixed-width fl-node-content\">\n\t\t\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-58b370b1ac30f\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac30f\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-58b370b1ac365 fl-col-has-cols\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac365\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-58b370b1ac3b8\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac3b8\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"fl-rich-text\">\n\t<p><strong>Candidates will remember you<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Our brains are wired to remember stories. And, more of the brain is activated when listening to a story, so the information is retained better. Are you going to remember a list of company benefits, or the story about how someone took two weeks off to help her rebuild her parents\u2019 house after Hurricane Katrina hit, thanks to a cool company policy?<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"fl-col-group fl-node-58b370b1ac421 fl-col-group-nested\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac421\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-58b370b1ac480 fl-col-small\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac480\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-vamtam-heading fl-node-58b370b1ac520\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac520\" data-progressive-animation=\"move-from-left\" data-vamtam-animation-options=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;progressive&quot;,&quot;origin&quot;:&quot;center center&quot;,&quot;exit&quot;:false,&quot;delay&quot;:0,&quot;mobile&quot;:false,&quot;pin&quot;:false,&quot;pinTrigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<h2 class=\"vamtam-heading \">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-line vamtam-heading-line-left\"><\/span>\n\t\n\t\n\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-text\">\u201cWhy, yes we can\u201d<\/span>\n\n\t\n\t\t\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-line vamtam-heading-line-right\"><\/span>\n\t<\/h2>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-vamtam-heading fl-node-58b370b1ac6c1\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac6c1\" data-progressive-animation=\"fade\" data-vamtam-animation-options=\"{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;progressive&quot;,&quot;origin&quot;:&quot;center center&quot;,&quot;exit&quot;:false,&quot;delay&quot;:0,&quot;mobile&quot;:true,&quot;pin&quot;:false,&quot;pinTrigger&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<h3 class=\"vamtam-heading \">\n\t\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/artofthetattoos?lang=bg\" title=\"@Conference\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\n\t<span class=\"vamtam-heading-text\">@Conference<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\n\t<\/h3>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"fl-col fl-node-58b370b1ac4ce\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac4ce\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-col-content fl-node-content\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-58b370b1ac58f\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac58f\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"fl-rich-text\">\n\t<p>\u201cWhy, yes we can,\u201d we said, and now that\u2019s all we do: gather stories from employees and use them to create content for recruitment marketing and employer branding.<\/p>\n<p>We really beat the drum on the story thing. We even named our company Stories Inc. But, why stories in the first place? It\u2019s all about your brain.  <\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<div class=\"fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-58b370b1ac5fa\" data-node=\"58b370b1ac5fa\">\n\t<div class=\"fl-module-content fl-node-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"fl-rich-text\">\n\t<p>Candidates will remember you<\/p>\n<p>Our brains are wired to remember stories. And, more of the brain is activated when listening to a story, so the information is retained better. Are you going to remember a list of company benefits, or the story about how someone took two weeks off to help her rebuild her parents&rsquo; house after Hurricane Katrina hit, thanks to a cool company policy?<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Adams also came to understand how important it was that his carefully crafted photos were reproduced to best effect. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":15630,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/03\/post-5.jpg","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1525"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1525"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1525\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15630"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/mann.vamtam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1525"}],"wp:term":[{"tax